Abel Gabuza (yin jiji to azán konukunatọ̀ntọ Whejisun, owhè 1955 tọn bo nọgbẹ̀ jẹ azán fọtọ̀nnúkunawetọ, Alunlunsun, owhè 2021 tọn) yin ogán sinsẹn Kátólíìkì tọn dé to South Africa Duban tọn sọn azán ṣinẹnẹtọ, Abòhúsun tọn to owhe 2018 kakajẹ okú etọn to owhe 2021 tọn mẹ. Ewọ wẹ Biṣọpu kindberley tọn sọn 2010 jẹ 2018. E yin jiji to Alexandra to South Africa.
Gabuza bẹ azọn bẹplamẹ COVID-19 tọn bo ku to azan fotọ̀nnúkunawetọ, Alunlunsun tọn to 2021 to owhè 65 mẹho yínyin mẹ to dotowhé Hillerest tọn to Duban.


